h1. grails-<script-name>

h2. Purpose

Allows execution of arbitrary Grails scripts from the Gradle command line.

h3. Description

{code}
$ gradle grails-refresh-dependencies
{code}

Pass arguments to Grails scripts

{code}
$ gradle grails-create-controller -PgrailsArgs="FooController"
{code}

Set environment for Grails script

{code}
$ gradle grails-run-app -PgrailsEnv=production
{code}